  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mentioned that--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The way they concealed the footprints.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The ingenious use of the sieve, and the snow in the sieve, yes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So Dora's father and her brother were both killed on one of the journeys to go out to get food, and that's why Dora, my future wife, became the sole person that was able to go out between those local population and acquire-- acquire food.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because she couldn't-- she couldn't be identified as a Jewess.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There are a couple of things I would like to go back to that I forgot to mention.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I did mention to you that my brother [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] was killed at the same time with my mother, my brother-in-law, my sister, and their child.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH ]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My brother was in camp Sasow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was, at the time, in the [GERMAN] in Zloczow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He got typhoid, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and he was brought to the hospital, which was in the vicinity of the [GERMAN] in Zloczow.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After he got a- slightly better, I was able to bring him some food, and paid off someone to let him go, instead of back-- instead of back to Sasow, to the camp, to my mother in the ghetto Zloczow for him to [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] be able to come back to-- to his health.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was a few days before the action in Zloczow, the liquidation of the Zloczow ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I still, up till today, live with [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] guilt that I was instrumental in him going to ghetto instead of going back to the camp, where he was killed with my mother, together.",
      "word_count": 37
    }
  ],
